                    Create a strong password to safeguard your account and sensitive information. Your password must be
                    <ul>
                        <li>at least 8 characters long,</li>
                        <li>include at least one uppercase letter (A-Z),</li>
                        <li>one lowercase letter (a-z),</li>
                        <li>one number (0-9), and</li>
                        <li>one special symbol (@,#,!,&,$,?,*).</li>
                    </ul>
                    Make sure to remember the password you create, as it will be required for future access.
